                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d578">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">853.51/364: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Portugal</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dearing</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lisbon</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1926-06-15T17:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 15, 1926—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received June 16—9:10 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>32. Department’s telegram 18, June 10, 2 p.m. Tobacco matter delayed by
                    revolution and vacancy Finance Portfolio but desired action promised this
                    week.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dearing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
